{{Quest rewards page|Animal Magnetism}}

==Required for completing==
Completion of Animal Magnetism is required for the following:
*[[Dragon Slayer II]]
*[[Lumbridge & Draynor Diary#Medium|Lumbridge & Draynor Medium Diary]]

